{"tid":858125,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【救市啦】權威人士倡設立萬億平準基金","createTime":"2018-10-11T14:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T00:58:49.000Z","uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa6e2ef8d8b46a2b910bf4a131794fa4b173ac0","tid":858125,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"據內地《財經雜誌》報道，已有權威人士和專家學者加緊調研，擬向監管層建議，希望再次考慮設立「萬億級股市平準基金」。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「平準基金」，可簡單理解成「干預基金」，它可對證券市場進行逆向操作，減低非理性的劇烈波動。主要是為了防止股市暴升暴跌，以穩定證券市場。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，除設立干預基金外，相關建議還包括進一步放寬保險資金和養老金的股市投資比例、改進股市分紅制度，提高現金分紅比例等，但目前證券監管部門尚未正面回應此事。<br />\n<br />\n突然又有萬億資金救市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6da7a5834d6c3bce30816609e981681710eb8d","tid":858125,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"聽日升1000點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e127dd625996ec69b27efc47b317305d5d61a637","tid":858125,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫估票架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af161d6d9265280220997cab00f61214d045a47","tid":858125,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e127dd625996ec69b27efc47b317305d5d61a637","tid":858125,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫估票架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"蠱惑嗰蠱"},{"pid":"64444919507fd79fec956da191406e1bab720eef","tid":858125,"uid":29851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DiciN5LU0AEorRS.jpg\" data